  "text": "One kilogram each; powder and paste were immersed for 24 hr in a 70:30 ethanol and distilled water solution in 5 L and 20 L Erlenmeyer flasks, respectively. The product was filtered through cotton cheese cloth in a plastic funnel and into a 3 L Erlenmeyer flask and concentrated by rotary evapovaporator (Büchi R-114) at 55 °C and 30 rpm [CITATION_1] ).",
